        "id": "2072393488411365572",
        "text": "If a workflow already has clear permissions, logs, and rollback, test Claude Sonnet 5 this week. If it relies on “ask Alex before doing anything,” wait. Agentic AI punishes fuzzy ops. #AI #DevTools",
        "url": "https://x.com/i/web/status/2072393488411365572",
