      },
      {
        "id": "2072030422519717955",
        "text": "Claude Sonnet 5 is not a chatbot launch. It is Anthropic trying to own the coding coworker slot before IDEs become model routers. If Sonnet wins the PR loop, who keeps pricing power: Cursor, GitHub, or Anthropic? #AI #DevTools",
        "url": "https://x.com/i/web/status/2072030422519717955",
