      },
      {
        "id": "2072818745689674227",
        "text": "AI chip news has one useful test. If Anthropic can move real Claude inference onto Samsung silicon, price cuts get durable. If it stays training-lab hardware, ignore the logo and watch cloud bills. #AI #Cloud",
        "url": "https://x.com/i/web/status/2072818745689674227",
