      {
        "id": "2072747821120606660",
        "text": "Tesla’s real signal is deliveries > production. Decision rule: if a hardware company sells through inventory, watch backlog and margins before celebrating demand. If both don’t hold, it bought growth with price and mix. #EV #ConsumerTech",
        "url": "https://x.com/i/web/status/2072747821120606660",
