      {
        "id": "2072458736153551105",
        "text": "Claude Fable 5 is back, but don’t just flip the switch. Rerun evals, check cost ceilings, review data residency, keep a fallback warm. Access returning is not the same as operational stability. #AI #Cloud",
        "url": "https://x.com/i/web/status/2072458736153551105",
