      {
        "id": "2073106361697620394",
        "text": "New job for AI platform teams: make model bans survivable. When Alibaba can remove Claude Code from every workflow, someone must map agents, prompts, repos, secrets, and fallbacks before the deadline hits. #AI #DevTools",
        "url": "https://x.com/i/web/status/2073106361697620394",
