      {
        "id": "2073180461581406360",
        "text": "The hidden cost of AI judgement: you must delete rules. Fable performs worse when every preference is pinned down. Good operators write the objective, the non-negotiables, and the review bar. #AI #DevTools",
        "url": "https://x.com/i/web/status/2073180461581406360",
